        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer425435361" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17592811344841132970">This is fantasy in a fairy tale kind of way for kids and I just have to say that this was such a cute little story. I enjoyed this one....and the ending....oh my. What a perfect set up for the next one. This is one book that I would read to my own kids if they were still little, especially my girls, but I think my boys would have thought it was kind of cool too. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


